data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 421 Lisbon Ave, Santa Paula, CA! This charming 4-bedroom, 2.5 - bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and location.  Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this home presents an excellent opportunity for families, first-time homebuyers, or anyone seeking a serene California retreat. The spacious and open living areas make this home perfect for entertaining. The living room flows seamlessly into the dining area and kitchen, creating an inviting atmosphere. The kitchen boasts modern stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar. Cooking and meal preparation will be a breeze in this well-appointed space. The three bedrooms are generously sized and filled with natural light. The main bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom for added privacy and convenience. Downstairs you will find a flex room that could easily be used as an office or possibly a 4th bedroom. The attached two-car garage provides parking and additional storage space, enhancing the functionality of the property. This home is situated in the highly sought after and friendly The Harvest at Limoneira Community with easy access to local schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining options. Santa Paula's charming downtown area is just a short drive away. The Harvest at Limoneira Community. POTENTIAL FOR VA BUYERS TO ASSUME VA LOAN AT 2.25% INTEREST RATE, CALL FOR MORE DETAILS!
